headline: CVS Health to hold fourth quarter and full year 2025 earnings conference call
summary: CVS Health® (NYSE: CVS) will hold a conference call with analysts and investors on Tuesday, February 10th, 2026, at 8:00 a.m. ET to discuss fourth quarter and full year 2025 financial results.

headline: WNC & Associates, Freeport Housing Trust, Best Apartments, Inc. and CVS Health Break Ground on Varney Heights, a 42-Unit Senior Housing Community in Freeport, Maine
summary: New development will expand affordable housing options for seniors ages 55+ amid growing regional demand Varney Heights Senior Housing Community WNC & Associates (WNC), a family-owned business known as both a pioneer and leader in the affordable housing industry, their investor CVS Health, and co-developers, Freeport Housing Trust and Best Apartments, Inc., have begun construction on Varney Heights, a 42-unit affordable housing community in Freeport, Maine.
